</p></a></div><div role="listitem" class="blog-card w-dyn-item"><div class="blog-heading ml-lg pos-relative hover-disable"><div>article</div></div><a data-w-id="a1483318-f83b-f15b-e5b5-29f52e7cfdd4" href="adobe-xd-design-examples-simple-and-inspiring-ideas" class="blog-card-link w-inline-block"><div class="blog-card-img-wrap blog-card-img-wrap--xl"><img alt="image" loading="lazy" data-w-id="a1483318-f83b-f15b-e5b5-29f52e7cfdd6" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/673c8eae5d232848cae90528_64a5379cd4b0a127dbe68d55_COVER_Adobe%2520XD%2520Design%2520Examples_%2520Simple%2520and%2520Inspiring%2520Ideas.png" class="blog-card-img"/></div><strong class="blog-card-title">Adobe XD Design Examples: Simple and Inspiring Ideas </strong><p class="blog-card-text">Why Adobe XD has turned into the number 1 design tool just within a few years? Learn more about Adobe XD best features with our short overview and helpful examples</p></a></div><div role="listitem" class="blog-card w-dyn-item"><div class="blog-heading ml-lg pos-relative hover-disable"><div>article</div></div><a data-w-id="a1483318-f83b-f15b-e5b5-29f52e7cfdd4" href="screen-design-examples" class="blog-card-link w-inline-block"><div class="blog-card-img-wrap blog-card-img-wrap--xl"><img alt="image" loading="lazy" data-w-id="a1483318-f83b-f15b-e5b5-29f52e7cfdd6" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a7a8b1268ea3f26dc72fad_Inspiring%20SaaS%20Landing%20Page%20Examples%20that%20Convert%C2%A0.png" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a7a8b1268ea3f26dc72fad_Inspiring%20SaaS%20Landing%20Page%20Examples%20that%20Convert%C2%A0-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a7a8b1268ea3f26dc72fad_Inspiring%20SaaS%20Landing%20Page%20Examples%20that%20Convert%C2%A0-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a7a8b1268ea3f26dc72fad_Inspiring%20SaaS%20Landing%20Page%20Ex